{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/hlS23ABq7d8BwAeB9LKfZ2Xum8L.jpg","belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":18,"name":"Drama"},{"id":53,"name":"Thriller"}],"homepage":"","id":11502,"imdb_id":"tt0056291","origin_country":["PL"],"original_language":"pl","original_title":"Nóż w wodzie","overview":"On their way to an afternoon on the lake, husband and wife Andrzej and Krystyna nearly run over a young hitchhiker. Inviting the young man onto the boat with them, Andrzej begins to subtly torment him; the hitchhiker responds by making overtures toward Krystyna. When the hitchhiker is accidentally knocked overboard, the husband's panic results in unexpected consequences.","popularity":1.1244,"poster_path":"/tkdeCwZhy9hzzVjZFjw0RPGWUIg.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":42243,"logo_path":null,"name":"Zespół Filmowy \"Kamera\"","origin_country":"PL"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"PL","name":"Poland"}],"release_date":"1962-03-09","revenue":0,"runtime":94,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[{"english_name":"Polish","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski"}],"status":"Released","tagline":"Acclaimed by all! Roman Polanski's tense, ironic Drama!","title":"Knife in the Water","video":false,"vote_average":7.278,"vote_count":475,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"AR","title":"El cuchillo bajo el agua","type":""},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","title":"Le couteau dans l'eau","type":""},{"iso_3166_1":"US","title":"Knife in the Water","type":""}]}}